Kevin, you became
C.E.O. of Saatchi

00:22:55.800 --> 00:22:57.730
having never worked
in an ad agency

00:22:57.730 --> 00:22:59.100
so the question is this.

00:22:59.100 --> 00:23:01.460
How, as an outsider,
do you come in

00:23:01.460 --> 00:23:04.460
and establish your
authority, your credibility

00:23:04.460 --> 00:23:07.560
and the fact that you are
someone to be respected

00:23:07.560 --> 00:23:09.700
but also not
to be terrorized by.

