I talked about our purpose

00:23:16.130 --> 00:23:18.800
which was to transform
the businesses' brands

00:23:18.800 --> 00:23:20.630
and reputations of our clients

00:23:20.630 --> 00:23:22.230
and I talked about our focus

00:23:22.230 --> 00:23:24.260
which was
to just make the best ads

00:23:24.260 --> 00:23:27.760
in the category
in every country we were in.

00:23:27.760 --> 00:23:29.760
So the story
that the first day in New York

00:23:29.760 --> 00:23:32.060
you walked through the office
with a baseball bat

