00:23:38.400 --> 00:23:40.500
One advantage that I had
at Saatchi  and  Saatchi...

00:23:40.500 --> 00:23:41.700
I had two advantages.

00:23:41.700 --> 00:23:43.130
One, I never worked
in advertising

00:23:43.130 --> 00:23:44.830
so that's a really good place
