00:23:44.830 --> 00:23:47.130
So I didn't know what could
be done, couldn't be done

00:23:47.130 --> 00:23:49.000
what should be done,
what shouldn't be done

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:50.200
any of that nonsense.

00:23:50.200 --> 00:23:53.160
When you came into this company

00:23:53.160 --> 00:23:55.530
um... I take it,
most people--

00:23:55.530 --> 00:23:56.560
as we established--

