00:24:17.460 --> 00:24:20.260
I had two previous track records
here in the U.K. marketplace

00:24:20.260 --> 00:24:22.760
dealing with
global businesses
and global enterprises.

00:24:22.760 --> 00:24:24.730
I see myself
as another member of the team.

00:24:24.730 --> 00:24:26.660
I've got a certain set
of responsibilities

00:24:26.660 --> 00:24:27.760
as these other people

00:24:27.760 --> 00:24:29.430
and if anyone misses
what we have to do

00:24:29.430 --> 00:24:30.760
the organization will miss.

00:24:30.760 --> 00:24:32.500
And the first couple of weeks
and months

00:24:32.500 --> 00:24:34.930
is just listen, listen, listen,
listen to these people

00:24:34.930 --> 00:24:36.300
and understand what's going on

00:24:36.300 --> 00:24:38.200
and then you kind of formulate
some views.

00:24:38.200 --> 00:24:39.600
Kevin, when I read
your speeches

00:24:39.600 --> 00:24:41.930
that you give literally
all over the world--

00:24:41.930 --> 00:24:44.500
I don't think you've
spoken in Antarctica

00:24:44.500 --> 00:24:46.360
but it's about the only
place you haven't--

00:24:46.360 --> 00:24:47.930
you really do talk
about what you do

00:24:47.930 --> 00:24:49.530
so much different
from a job.

00:24:49.530 --> 00:24:51.860
I mean, it does sound
to me almost like--

00:24:51.860 --> 00:24:53.430
as I said
at the beginning--

00:24:53.430 --> 00:24:55.860
an evangelist, I mean,
a passionate belief.

00:24:55.860 --> 00:24:58.860
Is this what drives you
more than anything else

00:24:58.860 --> 00:25:01.730
more than the material stuff,
more than...

00:25:01.730 --> 00:25:03.100
I mean, your wife and family

00:25:03.100 --> 00:25:04.600
live in New Zealand,
right?

00:25:04.600 --> 00:25:07.600
And you live there,
and New York
and London.

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:09.560
You get to spend how
much time with them?

00:25:09.560 --> 00:25:10.560
A week a month.

00:25:10.560 --> 00:25:12.400
What's wrong with that picture?

