I'd rather be doing this
than anything in the world.

00:25:40.530 --> 00:25:43.230
The chance to talk to you guys
is pretty exciting for me--

00:25:43.230 --> 00:25:45.160
To talk about what I believe in,
it's great.

00:25:45.160 --> 00:25:47.600
I don't think it's evangelism;
