you're probably going
to be really good at it

00:25:55.060 --> 00:25:56.630
if you're probably
really good at it

00:25:56.630 --> 00:25:58.530
you'll probably make
bucket loads of dough.

00:25:58.530 --> 00:26:00.330
And this is a great circle
to get into.

00:26:00.330 --> 00:26:01.500
Your wife will love that.

00:26:01.500 --> 00:26:03.430
You'll be able to do
great stuff with her--

00:26:03.430 --> 00:26:04.530
your husband, your kids.

00:26:04.530 --> 00:26:05.800
Passion.

00:26:05.800 --> 00:26:08.730
One more question
about corporate culture.

